			<li class="last"><a href="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/category/main-topics/legal/">Legal/Regulatory</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
		</header>
	<div class="a-column " id="a-col">
	<div id="content" class="hfeed">
	<article class="post-611448 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-investment-banking category-legal tag-banking-and-financial-institutions tag-bnp-paribas tag-credit-suisse-group-ag tag-federal-reserve-system tag-federal-taxes-us tag-holder-eric-h-jr tag-justice-department tag-lawsky-benjamin-m tag-office-of-the-comptroller-of-the-currency tag-tax-evasion per-holder-eric-h-jr per-lawsky-benjamin-m des-banking-and-financial-institutions des-federal-taxes-us des-tax-evasion org-bnp-paribas org-credit-suisse-group-ag org-federal-reserve-system org-justice-department org-office-of-the-comptroller-of-the-currency" id="post-611448">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
			<span class="kicker"><a href="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/category/main-topics/investment-banking/">Investment Banking</a> | <a href="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/category/main-topics/legal/">Legal/Regulatory</a></span>		</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Credit Suisse Pleads Guilty in Felony Case</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Ben Protess and Jessica Silver-Greenberg			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-05-19T20:50:50+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">May 19, 2014 4:50 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">May 19, 2014 4:50 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content">
	<div class="w592"><figure class="promo media video blog-video "
    data-videoid="100000002890350" data-media-action="modal" data-autoplay="" data-embedded="true" aria-label="media" role="group">
        <span class="visually-hidden">Video</span>

    <figcaption class="caption">
        <h4 class="headline">Holder Announces Credit Suisse Plea</h4>
