                <div class="summary-credit">
            <p class="summary">Attorney General Eric H. Holder Jr. announced that the Swiss bank would plead guilty in a tax evasion case, pay about $2.6 billion in penalties and hire an independent monitor.</p>
            <span class="credit video-credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder">
                By Associated Press on                                                    <span class="visually-hidden">Publish Date </span>May 19, 2014.
